features.feature_reason: Result of address verification system (AVS) used during checkout.
Transaction channel type (e.g., ecommerce or card-present).
Whether the transaction was international (higher risk and fees).
Outcome of CVV2 security check (match, no match, unavailable).
Electronic Commerce Indicator (ECI) reflects transaction security.
Merchant category code (defines merchant business type).
Method of card entry (manual, chip, swipe, contactless).
Security features supported by the terminal (e.g., EMV, NFC).
